ey\" with [[Karthi]], [[Kharesma Ravichandran]], [[Venkat Prabhu]] and [[Premgi Amaren]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/cha-cha-charey-from-party-single/1406698225 |title=Cha Cha Charey (From \"Party\")&nbsp;\u2013 Single |date=2 July 2018 |website=[[Apple Music]] |publisher=[[Muzik 247]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20180920141643/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/cha-cha-charey-from-party-single/1406698225 |archive-date=20 September 2018 |access-date=20 September 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2019\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Uriyadi 2]]''\n| Producer\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/teaser-of-suriya-produced-uriyadi-2-released-119032300279_1.html |title=Teaser of Suriya produced 'Uriyadi 2' released |date=2019-03-23 |work=[[Business Standard]] |access-date=2020-03-26 |url-status=live |agency=IANS}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2019\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Jackpot (2019 film)|Jackpot]]''\n| Producer\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/regional-cinema/story/jackpot-after-naachiyaar-jyothika-dons-khaki-again-for-suriya-s-film-1515032-2019-05-02 |title=Jackpot: After Naachiyaar, Jyothika dons khaki again for Suriya\u2019s film |date=May 2, 2019 |website=[[India Today]] |language=en |url-status=live |access-date=2020-03-26}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2019\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Sillu Karupatti]]''\n| Distributor\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/regional-movies/suriya-jyothika-throw-a-party-to-celebrate-50-day-run-of-sillu-karuppatti-see-pics/story-d0Eo44lZhLvKPdZZ4jX5SL.html |title=Suriya, Jyothika throw a party to celebrate 50-day run of Sillu Karuppatti, see pics |date=2020-02-24 |work=Hindustan Times |access-date=2020-03-26}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2020\n! scope=\"row\" |''[[Soorarai Pottru]]''\n| Producer, Playback singer\n| Sang the song \"Maara Theme\"\n|